{"tid":273882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為8,000元酬勞三港青運毒入泰國被捕","createTime":"2017-06-07T02:07:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T04:00:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ae1f7273cdd3a153f17a25d3419c14c3b87b36","tid":273882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:07:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20047211&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20047211%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170607&d=XXyqayngBpANlTYFuenLwE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8f95aab8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20047211%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170607&h=c1736192\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20047211&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170607</a><br />\n<br />\n為8,000元酬勞<br />\n三港青運毒入泰國被捕<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】3名90後香港青年為了8,000元酬勞，竟受僱跨國販毒集團當「衝關豬」，偷運毒品進入泰國，結果在曼谷機場被當地緝毒人員截獲，並在他們行李暗格內搜出12.3公斤可卡因，巿價約1,100萬港元，若罪成有機會被判終身監禁。<br />\n涉嫌入境運毒的3名港人，包括兩女一男（19至24歲），全部持香港特區護照入境。香港入境處發言人指事發後接獲其中一名24歲被捕男子的家屬求助，並已按其意願提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n三名香港青年日前在行李篋暗藏毒品偷運入泰國被捕。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n女毒販率先逃離返港<br />\n<br />\n據《泰國世界日報》報道，泰國毒品調查局上周六收到香港警方情報，指有毒販將一批毒品由巴西運往泰國，再轉運至香港。毒品調查局及泰國海關經調查後鎖定目標，周日截查3名由巴西乘飛機抵達曼谷蘇凡納布米國際機場的3名港人，並在其行李暗格內發現12.3公斤重的可卡因，巿值約5,000萬泰銖（約1,100萬港元）。<br />\n3人被捕後供稱，受僱一名叫「明姐」的香港女人，每人可獲約8,000港元作運毒報酬，原定過關後到曼谷巿素坤逸路一酒店房內交貨，泰國執法人員隨即掩至該酒店房搜查，發現人去樓空，估計「明姐」已聞風先遁。據悉「明姐」已乘機離境返港，泰國執法部門與香港警方合作，正追緝「明姐」及其他在逃人士。<br />\n■記者劉雲彪<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=XXyqayngBpANlTYFuenLwE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=3774b43e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"d91936716f4af2e7e5f41360852c6bc90033ec39","tid":273882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:08:23.000Z","msg":"三名香港青年日前在行李篋暗藏毒品偷運入泰國被捕。互聯網<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170607/large/a0403a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170607%2Flarge%2Fa0403a.gif&h=9b917dee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14da93f492a995f8eccacfa9c9317a7a8e5031ec","tid":273882,"uid":42429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:11:53.000Z","msg":"得8000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16d195ee337d24976564d8bb2b84feb6b8b131fa","tid":273882,"uid":7076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:26:27.000Z","msg":"你睇吓中間條女個Facebook就知道一定唔止＄8000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/wingyan.mina/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwingyan.mina%2F&d=XXyqayngBpANlTYFuenLwE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=4d255a0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/wingyan.mina/</a>"},{"pid":"2429bc3971e6b37e8f2e040d6119b756a1c484e0","tid":273882,"uid":5372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:27:57.000Z","msg":"包括兩女一男（19至24歲）???"},{"pid":"7095ecb841f9ccdccbb0dd9f7074abd6e85fd9d4","tid":273882,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"有排坐"},{"pid":"1207a8e9823e9fcb391aef454943d60e429a5390","tid":273882,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f909cbafc8362ef9211fca515802f91e010e84a","tid":273882,"uid":7